Description: Provides tools for processing and evaluating seasonal weather forecasts, with an emphasis on seasonal rainfall predictions for the Greater Horn of Africa.
    We follow the \href{https://library.wmo.int/doc_num.php?explnum_id=4886}{WMO recommendation of evaluating seasonal forecasts.} An online tutorial can be found \href{http://files.nr.no/samba/CONFER/SeaVal/}{here}.
    It is developed and maintained at the Norwegian Computing Center Oslo in collaboration with ICPAC.
    The development was supported by the European Unionâ€™s Horizon 2020 research and innovation programme under grant agreement no. 869730 (CONFER).
